
sequenceDiagram
autonumber

participant FE as Admin FE<br/>(Angular)
participant GW as Gateway<br/>(YARP)
participant AI as AI Service v2
participant OAI as OpenAI API
participant MCP as Monolith MCP
participant MON as Monolith API
participant OBX as Outbox Processor
participant CON as Connector API<br/>(Saga)
participant USR as User API
participant CMP as Company API
participant JOB as Job API
participant KC as Keycloak

Note over FE,KC: Scenario: Admin says "Create a company called Acme Corp"<br/>AI selects create_company tool, provisions across 7 services in ~5.5s

Note over FE,KC: Phase 1 — Chat request + tool selection (0ms → 2,327ms)

FE->>+GW: POST /ai/v2/chat
GW->>+AI: proxy → ai-service-v2
AI->>+OAI: POST /v1/chat/completions
Note right of OAI: Tool selection<br/>1,601ms
OAI-->>-AI: tool_call: create_company

Note over FE,KC: Phase 2 — MCP tool execution + CQRS command pipeline

AI->>+MCP: tools/call → create_company
Note over MCP: Validate (~60ms)<br/>Direct DB queries (job-board-monolith)<br/>• Company name uniqueness<br/>• Company email uniqueness<br/>• Admin email uniqueness<br/>• Industry existence
Note over MCP: Atomic transaction (~234ms)<br/>• Create company entity<br/>• Create admin user<br/>• Write outbox message<br/>• Commit once
Note right of MCP: Monolith MCP shares codebase + DB.<br/>No HTTP call to Monolith API.
MCP-->>-AI: tool result (success, ~531ms)

AI->>+OAI: POST /v1/chat/completions
Note right of OAI: Response generation<br/>1,292ms
OAI-->>-AI: "Company Acme Corp created..."
AI-->>-GW: 200 OK (streamed)
GW-->>-FE: chat response

Note over FE,KC: Phase 4 — Outbox → Pub/Sub (~1,090ms poll gap + 24ms)

Note over OBX: Poll picks up message #790
OBX->>CON: Dapr pub/sub<br/>company.created.v1<br/>(CloudEvent)

Note over FE,KC: Phase 5 — Provisioning saga (4,035ms → 5,555ms)

activate CON
Note over CON: Idempotency check (3ms)

CON->>+MON: GET /odata/companies({id})
MON-->>-CON: 200 (company data)
CON->>+MON: GET /odata/users({id})
MON-->>-CON: 200 (admin data)
Note over CON: Saga: fetch data complete (232ms)

Note over FE,KC: Phase 6 — Parallel fan-out via Dapr service invocation

par Dapr → user-api (1,440ms)
CON->>+USR: POST /api/companies<br/>(Dapr invoke)

Note over USR,KC: Phase 7 — Keycloak provisioning (1,389ms)

USR->>+KC: GET /groups (list groups)
KC-->>-USR: 200 (12ms)
USR->>+KC: POST /groups/.../children<br/>(company group)
KC-->>-USR: 201 (19ms)
USR->>+KC: POST /groups/.../children<br/>(CompanyAdmins)
KC-->>-USR: 201 (14ms)
USR->>+KC: POST /groups/.../children<br/>(Recruiters)
KC-->>-USR: 201 (9ms)
USR->>+KC: GET /users (check existing)
KC-->>-USR: 200 (10ms)
USR->>+KC: POST /users (create user)
KC-->>-USR: 201 (269ms)
USR->>+KC: PUT /users/{id}/groups/{gid}
KC-->>-USR: 204 (12ms)
USR->>+KC: PUT /users/{id}/send-verify-email
KC-->>-USR: 204 (36ms)

Note over USR: Persist user + company<br/>records (987ms)

USR-->>-CON: 200 OK
and Dapr → company-api (1,133ms)
CON->>+CMP: POST /api/companies<br/>(Dapr invoke)
Note over CMP: Create company<br/>projection
CMP-->>-CON: 200 OK
and Dapr → job-api (268ms)
CON->>+JOB: POST /api/companies<br/>(Dapr invoke)
Note over JOB: Create company<br/>projection
JOB-->>-CON: 204 No Content
end

Note over FE,KC: Phase 8 — Company activation (5,484ms → 5,537ms)

USR-)CMP: Dapr pub/sub<br/>provision.user.success

CON->>+MON: POST /api/companies/<br/>company-created-success
Note over MON: ActivateCompanyCommand<br/>(128ms)

Note over FE,KC: Phase 9 — Real-time notification

MON--)FE: SignalR: CompanyActivated<br/>(3ms send + receive)
MON-->>-CON: 200 OK

Note over FE: UI updates in real-time<br/>company.name = "Acme Corp"

Note over FE,KC: Phase 10 — Saga complete (5,555ms)

Note over CON: Saga finalized ✓<br/>Company provisioned
deactivate CON

